Text.string: Let me out!
Citizen, I cannot release you unless your fine is paid in full.
Damn it! To hell with you!
Cursing is a class-one offense. You have been fined an additional $5,000.
You're a lightbulb plugged into a shit box. I ain't payin'!
Citizen, thank you for choosing the Fecapod.
When I get outta here, I'm gonna take a deuce on your processor!
Threatening fecal crimes is a class-seven offense.
Raaagh!
Citizen, all Fecapods are equipped with standard issue anti-incendiary plating. Our motto is “let's keep the fire in the hole!”
Hey, someone out there? Get me out! This shitter's holding me hostage!
Citizen, you are currently prohibited from exiting this Fecapod because you are in possession of an illegally-obtained firearm. That is a class-five offense.
Open the damn door, ya talking turd-closet! It stinks in here.
Look, this AI won't let me leave. Help me out, and I'll give you a contraband gun.
I'm dyin' in here!

Name's Trashmouth. All you have to do is swap this shit-sipping AI's chip for one with a looser interpretation of the law. Like a dirty copbot. They're always harassing my crew for bribes. My crew will help ya get me outta here. Go find 'em!
If you don't get me out soon, I'm gonna put this sweet contraband gun to my head and pull the trigger!
Let me out right now!
Citizen, you are agitated. Emergency calming protocols initiated.
Gahhhgahhhh!
Your leader is swimming in crap. Told me to find you.
Your leader's stuck on the pot, lovelies. Told me to find you.
Your dauntless leader is trapped in a fecal pool and requests aid.
Your leader's trapped in a crapper with a contraband zapper. Needs help.
Trashmouth ain't the leader. Fecking traitor stole my favorite gun and split!
Kill this scrub!
Your fine can be paid in cash or select bodily fluids, depending on service provider.
Traitors! Wipe 'em!
They dead? Don't care. Grab a can and come back here.
Great, now just smash a window or two and the pigs'll come runnin' for the slop.
I love the sound of breaking glass! Here they come!
Citizen, that is a class-four offense. Cram some cash in my hush box, or you are under arrest.
Ah, dirty bots love their hush money! I can respect that. Almost. Now cut it open and scoop out its dirty chip.
Grab that AI chip!
Good. Now, come on back and plug that new AI into this crap-silo.
Hurry up! My lungs are full of methane and day old ratchwich, extra whiskers. It's like modern art in here, and that ain't pretty.
Tampering with a Fecapod is a class-two offense punishable by...
Open the door!
Where the hell am I? Ohh, goddammit!
That's right! Let me out of here! We're in this together now!
Ah, what have we here? Illegal firearm. You want out, citizen? It's gonna cost ya.
I ain't paying you crap!||—Actually, that's all I CAN pay you right now.
Calling in back up... code 2589, man on a crapper. We got some primo extortion targets here!
Damn, we got company. Take 'em out, we'll talk after.
Okay, fellas. Let's shake down this perp.
While you were fighting, I got me an idea. Waste management bots are the lowest on the Promethea-bot food chain. Total pushovers. Make a mess, and one of them will come running.
Here we go!
A fecal fountain! Oh, glorious day!
Citizen, this Fecapod's ventilation system is currently not operational.
[humming happily]
Cute. Kill it.
Grab the chip.
Good, install it.
Hey, what the hell?
This better work. If there is a hell, I'm up to my waist in it already.
Oh boy, what a mess! I can't possibly clean this on my own! I'm in over my head, here!
Yo bot, let me out of here, then you and your buddies can clean out this crapbox all you want.
I appreciate your confidence, citizen, but this is beyond my abilities. Your feces is a level twenty-seven biohazard. I can't risk contamination.
Contamination? I'm up to my ears in my own damn feces! Let me out!
When I get outta here, I'm gonna crap all over your AI chip!
Attention, nearby citizen. Assist me in patching up this here Fecapod, and you will be rewarded for your efforts.
Keep this up, and I'll make you an honorary member of the Poop Crew!
I'll... pass on that promotion.
Um... no.
Ho ho! But I must decline.
Ahh, been there, done that. I'm good.
Let me out!
Emergency protocols initiated. Altering chemical composition of methane gas.
What's going on?
All Fecapods are equipped with self-guidance sequencers. I hope I have enough methane to get to mainline waste processing.
No-no-no-no no no NO!
All right, we gotta get the pigbot's attention. So tag that building!
Threatening a government AI is a class-two offense.
You gotta vandalize that building.
Blast off in three, two, one...
Goddammit.
Huh. Wonder where he went? I want that gun!
Wonder where he blasted off to...
That stench should not be hard to follow.
Oof. Wouldn't wanna be him. Wonder where he landed?
Hell yeah, sweet freedom!
Citizen, this Fecapod has been illegally installed on a motor vehicle. Please assist me.
What the hell? We got a tail—kill that friend of a shit-sipper!
If you don't let me out, I'm gonna die in here!
Hurry up, you bastards! Faster!
Get this junk heap moving! The Vault Hunter's tailing us!
Ahhhh, are you TRYING to kill me?
Faster! Faster!
Citizen, this Fecapod has been compromised. You must sanitize it.
I'll sanitize you, you crap-gargling crap bot!
Keep goin'! Fire is the ultimate sterilizer!
Cram it, you turd-farming bastard!
Just a little more, citizen!
Ugh! Drive faster! I don't wanna die in this shit sipper!
Dying in a city-issued Fecapod is a class-three offense.
Craaaaaaaaap!
Goodbye, citizen! Keep Promethea... clean...
